at master · glinscott/nnue-pytorch · GitHub - HalfKAv2 feature set</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-6\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-6\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://github.com/official-stockfish/Stockfish/pull/3203\">Optimization of the affine transformations. by Sopel97 · Pull Request #3203 · official-stockfish/Stockfish · GitHub</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-7\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-7\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://github.com/official-stockfish/Stockfish/pull/3218\">AVX-512 optimizations. by Sopel97 · Pull Request #3218 · official-stockfish/Stockfish · GitHub</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-8\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-8\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://github.com/official-stockfish/Stockfish/pull/3663\">Optimize and tidy up affine transform code. by Sopel97 · Pull Request #3663 · official-stockfish/Stockfish · GitHub</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-9\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-9\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://github.com/glinscott/nnue-pytorch/pull/1\">Defer data preparation to native code. Use sparse input tensors. · Pull Request #1 · glinscott/nnue-pytorch · GitHub</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-10\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-10\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://github.com/glinscott/nnue-pytorch/pull/96\">A custom kernel for the feature transformer. · Pull Request #96 · glinscott/nnue-pytorch · GitHub</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-11\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-11\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"referenc